{
  "stem": "5430.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard the progress that the Russian armies made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also heard a lot of the American advances.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because all of a sudden, we had a lot of goods from the United States that filtered down over their, clothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were intended for the Polish people, Polish citizens, I should say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whether they filtered down to us or not, but it was available, and it started coming down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that by the end of the war, we were allowed to return-- repatriate back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only problem is, I have no papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In order to travel in the-- in the Soviet Union, you gotta have a permit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somehow or other, my father was able to-- by that time, he was well, and he was able to negotiate with the local [INAUDIBLE], the chief, to give me a special permit to get out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so that's right, all you had to do is schmear them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And by the time we got back to Poland-- well, first we were on the train all away from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Belovodsk to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was the Trans-Siberian train-- not the Trans-Siberian, the southern train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, we got to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "From Moscow, we got to Lviv, excuse me, which is Lemberg, and we stayed there a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the meantime--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously, not-- not so terribly bad, because it doesn't stand out in my mind as to--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is why I say when we got back from Lviv, we got into Poland, we came into Selmentsi, it's the border town for Poland and the Ukraine, and the first greeting we got from the Pollacks was, dirty Jews, you survived?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hitler didn't get you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was our greetings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, my brother--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
